{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act33side_level_act33side_04_end","storyGroup":"act33side","storySort":9,"storyDependence":"act33side_level_act33side_04_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BB-4","storyName":"悠长的旅途","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"博士带着阿米娅回到了巴别塔，决定以巴别塔一员的身份帮助阿米娅和其他感染者。特蕾西娅则向博士展示了自己利用源石创造的“希望”。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act33side/level_act33side_04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act33side_04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":8,"next":10,"characters":["凯尔希","可露希尔","？？？","阿米娅","特蕾西娅","博士"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_bg_bg_corridor_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"1091年秋","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"卡兹戴尔地区，巴别塔罗德岛本舰","id":10},{"type":"dialog","id":11},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可露希尔，进度如何？","id":14,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我不希望这次还会出现本舰核心系统失控的问题。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":16},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_050","duration":"1","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"1.2","id":18},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"唔......哈哈，你非要说呢，那可能还是遇到了一些小小的问题来着。","id":20,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"就算拿着你给我的锦囊妙计，PRTS的很多程序加密模式也不是常人能理解的啊。我的解码仪器还不能完全适配。","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"就结果而言，可能来不及在博士登舰前完全关闭系统。","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"再尝试一次。","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"如果还是没有把握，就准备应急方案......完全切断本舰的所有能源。","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"放心交给我吧！","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"不过......看来你还藏了很多秘密呢，凯尔希。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"我从来没有见过有人能让你如此紧张。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......这不重要，可露希尔。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"重要的是，我不希望本舰出现任何意外。","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"唔，可按照阿斯卡纶传回的任务简报来看，博士只是一个普通人，还是一个会背着落难小兔子到处瞎逛的大善人。","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"我们好像没有必要这么防备他吧？","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"威胁并不来自博士。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"那是啥？","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你还不需要知道。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"为了博士的安全，也为了巴别塔成员的安全，抹除他的登舰记录。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"在博士和特蕾西娅得出结论前，不必让其他成员知道他的存在。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"好好好，我再加把劲......","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"可是明明你一副很在意博士的样子，却又这么警惕那个人......","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"啊——难道博士抓住了你的什么把柄！","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不要想着调查，你查不到。","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"呃。不用这么严肃吧。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#14$1","focus":"l","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"还有......那个被救下的孩子，她的身份？","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"还是老结论。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"我反复核对了当时与雷姆必拓有关的一切记录，还让Scout和军事委员会的内应做了确认。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"阿米娅的身份没有问题。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"她的父母的确是在为我们运送激光开采模块的车队里遇袭身亡，针对他们的袭击是绝对的意外。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"没有人知道他们运送的是和萨卡兹有关的货物，而那场袭击也并非军事委员会的刻意安排。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"而她应该也是在这场事故中才成了感染者。如果不是博士......她可能会在雷姆必拓凄惨地度过余生吧。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我会亲自负责那个孩子登舰后的检查和治疗方案。","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"你还是不放心那个孩子吗？","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不放心。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"她年纪太小，感染矿石病后没经过像样的治疗。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"是这种“不放心”喔。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_050.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我不希望博士的善意变成拖延她治疗的罪魁祸首，而且......","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......特蕾西娅会说，她是个善良的孩子，有权利选择未来。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":73},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":74},{"type":"charslot","id":75},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":76},{"type":"gridbg","imagegroup":"38_g20_skyblue_L1/38_g20_skyblue_r1/38_g20_skyblue_L2/38_g20_skyblue_r2","solidwidth":"1280/1280/1280/1280","solidheight":"720/720/720/720","x":"-1200","id":77},{"type":"largebgtween","duration":"60","yFrom":"500","yTo":"720","block":"false","id":78},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"阿米娅，阿米娅。","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......好困......我......我在哪？","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士......博士？","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"博士就在这。","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"小懒虫，快醒醒，你快要到家了。","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"家？","id":86},{"type":"text","text":"迷迷糊糊地，阿米娅感受到温暖的指尖在脸颊旁移动。","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"好痒，哈哈，不要挠我的脖子。","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"呀！","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你、你是谁？","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"特蕾西娅。我是特蕾西娅。","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"特蕾西娅......博士和我提起过你......","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"哦，博士怎么说我呢？","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"唔，忘记了......不过我当时在吃很好吃的胡萝卜蛋糕......","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"特蕾西娅应该是......香香的......甜甜的......热腾腾的。","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"那现在呢？特蕾西娅和你想象的样子一样吗？","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯......也是香香的......甜甜的......热腾腾的，就是没有胡萝卜味......","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"呵呵，看来还没睡醒呢。","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"小阿米娅，要和我们一起回家吗？","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"家......嗯......好......","id":100},{"type":"dialog","id":101},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_dim_closeeye","layer":"1","id":102},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":103},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":104},{"type":"bgeffect","id":105},{"type":"gridbg","id":106},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_bg_bg_desert_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":107},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":109},{"type":"text","text":"卡兹戴尔地区，巴别塔罗德岛本舰外","id":110},{"type":"dialog","id":111},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":112},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","duration":"1","id":113},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":114},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":115},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅的怀中，小小的卡特斯正环着她的脖子酣睡。","id":116},{"type":"text","text":"她轻轻拍拍阿米娅的后背，转头看向一旁显得有些疲惫的博士。","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"谢谢你专程离舰来接我们......特蕾西娅。","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"看来你也不是无所不知的，博士。","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"至少在照顾小孩子这方面，你还有很多要学的东西。","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......当然。","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你看上去和离开时很不一样了，博士。这趟旅程怎么样？","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我见到了很多，也学到了很多......在这片大地上所见到的都很有趣。","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"以及，我遇见了阿米娅......在那场事故中救下她，简直算得上奇迹。","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"阿米娅。她的确比信中写的还要可爱。可怜的孩子，但也算幸运。","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"她的病情不可避免地在变严重，我需要带她回来接受治疗。","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我离开的这段时间，巴别塔......","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"算不上顺利，我们遇到了许多问题，但并不急在这一时去解决。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"经过那么漫长的旅途，你们一定很累了，请先休息一下吧。","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"非常感谢，特蕾西娅。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"阿米娅，我们到家了。","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":142},{"type":"charslot","id":143},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":144},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"唔......博士，你在叫我吗......我是不是睡着了？","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":147},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":148},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"呀，小阿米娅，你醒了。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"阿米娅，下来好不好？特蕾西娅一直抱着你会累的。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":153},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":154},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"5","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":155},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅乖巧地点点头，从特蕾西娅的怀中跃下，站在地上蹦了蹦。","id":156},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","duration":"1","posfrom":"-100,0","posto":"-100,0","id":158},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":159},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","duration":"1","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"100,0","id":160},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":161},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"那阿米娅可以牵着我吗？","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士......？","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"可以的。特蕾西娅是我的朋友，是值得信任的人，之后，她也会陪着你很长时间。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯......","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":170},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"50,0","duration":"0.8","id":171},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":172},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这就是巴别塔吗？","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"嗯。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"好大啊，比那些采矿地块还要大......原来博士以前生活在这种地方。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我在这里生活了很久......很久，阿米娅。","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这里是博士的家吗？","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"没错，阿米娅，这里是博士生活过很久的家。对吧，博士？","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......是的。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"以后这里也会是你的家，让我们和博士一起照顾你，好不好？","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"好......博士在哪，我就在哪。","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":193},{"type":"dialog","id":194},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":195},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rampartclose","text":"","id":196},{"type":"charslot","id":197},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"1","grad":"true","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/97/Avg_49_i15.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":199},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"2","vibrato":"50","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":200},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":201},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"1","fillto":"0","block":"false","fadetime":"6","id":202},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":203},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$newhope02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_newhope02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":204,"musicid":1},{"type":"text","text":"他们踏上了眼前的升降平台，巴别塔的标志缓缓出现在他们的眼前。","id":205},{"type":"text","text":"那扇沉重的大门缓缓打开，迎接着他们的到来。","id":206},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅感受到了阿米娅的胆怯，轻轻扶住了她的肩膀。","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这扇门后面......是什么样呀？","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"在那后面，都是欢迎阿米娅与博士的人。","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"你不会犹豫吗，特蕾西娅？正式接纳我，还有这个孩子。","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"有什么好犹豫的呢？我很高兴，巴别塔可以成为很多人的家。","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"只不过，这里许多人都还不认识你，接下来你恐怕会度过很忙碌的几天了。","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我应该以什么身份出现在他们面前？","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这的确很伤脑筋。但我想，你可以先和凯尔希聊聊，她一直在等着你。","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士，你的顾虑，你的疑问，还有你藏在心底里的秘密，去和凯尔希说说吧。","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"否则她会很难过的。","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"你本可以......","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"如果你真的希望“魔王”来揭开你不愿倾诉的心思，我会这么做的。但我感觉到，你还在犹豫。","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"走吧，阿米娅，博士，让我们去见她。","id":220},{"type":"dialog","id":221},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":222},{"type":"charslot","id":223},{"type":"image","id":224},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gatecloz","text":"","id":225},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":226},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_bg_bg_corridor_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":227},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":228},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":229},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#11$1","duration":"1","id":230},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"阿米娅。你就是阿米娅，对吗？","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#8$1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯......","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":235},{"type":"text","text":"凯尔希蹲了下来，从兜中掏出一颗早已备好的糖果递给女孩。","id":236},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":237},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"阿米娅，感谢你一路上保护着博士。","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"谢谢......凯尔希医生。","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可以去找特蕾西娅小姐吗？我们得为你做一些检查。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"检查......会痛吗？","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"会痛，但我知道你是坚强的孩子，博士已经写信告诉我了。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士会陪着我吗？","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"当然，不过博士有一些工作需要先处理。","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":254},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"没事的阿米娅。在病房里等我一会，我很快就会去找你的。","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":257},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":258},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......好。","id":260,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9d/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":261},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":262},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":263},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":264},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博士，之后你也需要做全身的检查。","id":266,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":267},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"好的。","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......博士。","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"嗯？","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"之后你还打算再离开吗？","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"不会了，我想这趟旅程已经足够。","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#11$1","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"如果你已经下定决心的话，我尊重你的选择。","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"至少，你很在意阿米娅的健康......哪怕她与你本无交集。","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"这些新生命与我们也并无本质差异。","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#11$1","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......很高兴。","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你始终选择了希望。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#13$1","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"欢迎回来，Dr.{@nickname}。","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":288},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"charslot","id":290},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":291},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_bg_bg_infirmary.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":292},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_devicebeep","channel":"bgs","loop":"true","id":294},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":295},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":296},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":297},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":298},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":299},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"阿米娅还好吗？","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"血液里源石含量始终很高，目前阻断剂的效力还远远达不到控制病情的程度。","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"必须要研发新一代的药物......我需要一些资源和时间。","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"巴别塔的所有资源自始至终都向你敞开，博士。我们很乐意向你开放现阶段对于矿石病的所有研究。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......作为交换，我能帮上你和凯尔希什么忙？","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这并非交换，这是巴别塔建立的初衷之一，我们会力所能及地帮助每一个矿石病患者。","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"从凯尔希唤醒你的那天起，我就相信你会帮助我们所有人，就像你会帮助阿米娅那样。","id":311,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......谢谢。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士，或许我现在终于有机会问你那个问题。","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你如何看待这片大地？","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我想我还没有资格去点评些什么。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"文明并没有高低优劣之分，如今的泰拉文明，同样是经历漫长且艰辛的时光才演变成现在的样子。","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"而源石又和所有生命开了一个无比恶劣的玩笑......","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我记得你说过，现在的源石并不符合最初的预期。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"在我原本的期待里，它本不该带来这些苦难。","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"（睡梦中的呓语）","id":326},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我能感觉到，你隐藏着一些秘密。可是你心底那股我无法理解的......悲悯，也绝非作假。","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我想修复这个错误，可现在的我无能为力......","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"何况文明的进程大都相似，无论人们如何挣扎，无论其光芒在某一瞬间有多么璀璨......终点恐怕都显而易见。","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"可凯尔希说过，在最后的日子里，你们亦不曾放弃希望。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"在最后的岁月里，我同样有许多朋友，他们面临着远超你想象的难题和困扰，也心怀着......比你们有过之而无不及的斗志和希望。","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"可他们，也无一例外，失败，消亡。","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......特蕾西娅。我们相处的时间还不算长，我想知道，你做这一切的底气是什么？","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"巴别塔向军事委员会妥协，是为了等一个什么样的结果？","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":343,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士，我有东西想给你看。","id":345,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"关于源石，我们迟早都要向你请教答案。这也是凯尔希唤醒你的原因。","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"希望你能来看看......我短暂努力的结果。","id":347,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":348},{"type":"dialog","id":349},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":350},{"type":"charslot","id":351},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":352},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8b/Avg_bg_bg_thundercloud.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":353},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":355},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我们快要到了......","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......这附近只有一片荒芜，甚至在天灾多发地区都算得上极端。但看得出，可露希尔甚至有抽出手来维护这条小径，危险的小道......","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"源石簇之间的分叉小径，特蕾西娅，你的秘密也不比我少。","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"谁让我是“魔王”呢。","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士，接下来你看到的东西，请不要跟任何人说起。","id":361},{"type":"dialog","id":362},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"charslot","id":364},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_49_i22.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","id":365},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"60","block":"false","id":366},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":367},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$ghosthunter_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_ghosthunter_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":368,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":369},{"type":"text","text":"在源石晶簇遍布的荒野上跋涉许久，访客见到了一小片花圃。","id":370},{"type":"text","text":"在天灾中央，在毁灭之间，在晚霞与星河都寻觅不到的无名原野上。","id":371},{"type":"text","text":"星星点点的白色小花圈出了一方遗世独立的圣地，与周遭的环境隔绝开来。蛮荒的一切都与这里无关，连风也变得柔软。","id":372},{"type":"text","text":"像是被时间遗忘的温室，保留着遥远的过去纤尘不染的模样。","id":373},{"type":"text","text":"像是人类第一次从神明那里偷来火光，照亮了苍茫夜空的一角。","id":374},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅捧起了一朵纯白的花。","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这就是我，也是巴别塔对源石最深入的研究。","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"花......？","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"不，是“源石”。","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"——","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你应该能意识到，这并不是催出花朵的源石技艺。","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"来自源石之中的信息，来自内化宇宙的反转......","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"你们对源石的研究，已经到了这一步？什么时候......","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"萨卡兹是最了解源石的种族，即便如此，比起源石的全部，我们所知不过是冰山一角。","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"即使有凯尔希协助我们钻研源石的本质，我们费尽心思、穷尽心血所做到的，也仅仅是将一块巴掌大的活性源石，转化为这样的......","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"一片花圃。","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"一种希望。","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这朵小小的白花，只是我的一点努力。我也想请求博士你的帮助。","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我想看花海倒灌，涌出卡兹戴尔的断崖和山谷，直到开满大地的那一天。","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......那个未来，值得我们去冒险。","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士，正如你所见，卡兹戴尔，长久以来都陷在战争的泥沼中。","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"至少当下，我想用源石的这种能力，为卡兹戴尔开辟一片可以不受外敌侵扰的家园。人们可以留在这里安居乐业，不用再以战场为家。","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"而在更遥远的将来......如果有一天，我们可以完全控制源石，整片大地的模样都会被改变吧。","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"假如天灾发生时，天空中落下的不是源石晶簇，而是软绵绵的云朵。","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"假如感染者身上也不再长出石头......","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"大概不会有人做这样荒唐的幻梦吧......","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......作为一个萨卡兹，你确实与众不同，特蕾西娅。","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"开满大地的花......","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......那会是一副生机勃勃的景象。","id":399},{"type":"dialog","id":400},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":401},{"type":"charslot","id":402},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":403},{"type":"image","id":404},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","id":405},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":406},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_bg_bg_desert_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":407},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":408},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":409},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......","id":411,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士？","id":413,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"为什么......是这样一朵花？","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"啊......没什么特别的原因，峡谷外面生长着这种花，我第一次寻找合适的实验地点时，看到了而已。","id":417,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"只是无意的。","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"凯尔希说，这种花曾有个名字，叫夏雪草。","id":419,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"不过经历了这么多年的环境变化，它也在适应，也许，它也可以有一个新的名字。","id":420,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你觉得呢，博士？","id":421,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1360_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......","id":423,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我......","id":424,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_1360_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":425},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":426},{"type":"charslot","id":427},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":428},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":429},{"type":"sticker","id":430,"text":"新的道路正在打开。","x":"320","y":"340","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"1"},{"type":"sticker","id":431,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":432},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_signlntrfrnc","volume":"0.8","id":433},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_signalInterference","layer":"1","id":434},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_bg_bg_white.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","id":435},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":436},{"type":"sticker","id":437,"text":"<color=#000000>一条自毁之路。</color>","x":"320","y":"340","alignment":"center","size":"22","delay":"0.001","width":"700","block":"true","duration":"1"},{"type":"sticker","id":438,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":439},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":440},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":441},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":442},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.4","id":443},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"特蕾西娅，能听到吗？","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我在听。我正在带博士参观我们的......","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"卡兹戴尔传回来一些紧急消息，必须立刻让你知晓。","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......与维多利亚有关。","id":448},{"type":"dialog","id":449},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":450},{"type":"image","id":451},{"type":"charslot","id":452}],"characters":["凯尔希","可露希尔","？？？","阿米娅","特蕾西娅","博士"]}